{"tid":399073,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"生蛇後兩個月仲痛緊","createTime":"2017-09-13T15:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T10:36:32.000Z","uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3dfe9f45af4d4c149c915b409c1db0d2f56e20a","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"小弟7月尾生蛇<br />\n好生唔生生係右額度 聽聞係最難搞<br />\n<br />\n初初已經睇私家食左特效藥<br />\n1個星期後啲蛇都好番好多 但原來先係惡夢的開始 ....<br />\n生蛇嘅位置持續地痛 好難形容 <br />\n係針拮痛 閃電痛 仲開始影響眼<br />\n總之十級痛 生不如死<br />\n<br />\n呢2 個月 不停咁睇醫生 眼科<br />\n好在最後眼無事 但痛仍然持續<br />\n醫生都開始無乎 只係開啲神經止痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後無計可施 走左去睇針灸<br />\n針左大約5 次 先有少少轉機 ...<br />\n痛嘅程度係有減輕 但痛仍然無停過<br />\n好想可以100%回復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴打有相同經歷可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同跪求神醫既幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n任何方法我都會試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cf861800512419532d0df21875d2e855613c2f","tid":399073,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpostherpetic-neuralgia%2Fpages%2Fintroduction.aspx&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7416667f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a714ac70e5169a5093d8ffa17d1b47eba5ee2fc6","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpostherpetic-neuralgia%2Fpages%2Fintroduction.aspx&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7416667f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入面話年紀大先會咁<br />\n小弟27 歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b007425a93e59e22d6fd08fa788aeb033b1d03fd","tid":399073,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"用左類固醇藥未"},{"pid":"00106b2399e644ac6c16965fe2145974a6c0c32d","tid":399073,"uid":86702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用左類固醇藥未</blockquote><br />\nfor skin lesion ?<br />\nwouldnt use systemic steroid ?"},{"pid":"bdfe26630a9ecd329673f88471c7bc143faf939c","tid":399073,"uid":86702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpostherpetic-neuralgia%2Fpages%2Fintroduction.aspx&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7416667f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入面話年紀大先會咁<br />\n小弟27 歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMcp1403062%23t%3Darticle&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f493cf4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article</a><br />\nThere is currently no disease-modifying therapy for postherpetic neuralgia8; thus, treatment is based on symptom control. Because pain may persist for years or for life, medication is often required over prolonged periods. It is important to monitor the effect of interventions on pain intensity (with the methods described above) and to modify or discontinue treatments that do not result in appreciable pain relief or that have adverse effects in excess of the benefit."},{"pid":"f810ce7cc713653e127786c10d89959b0818df64","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpostherpetic-neuralgia%2Fpages%2Fintroduction.aspx&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7416667f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入面話年紀大先會咁<br />\n小弟27 歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMcp1403062%23t%3Darticle&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f493cf4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article</a><br />\nThere is currently no disease-modifying therapy for postherpetic neuralgia8; thus, treatment is based on symptom control. Because pain may persist for years or for life, medication is often required over prolonged periods. It is important to monitor the effect of interventions on pain intensity (with the methods described above) and to modify or discontinue treatments that do not result in appreciable pain relief or that have adverse effects in excess of the benefit.</blockquote><br />\n即係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58265f78f984b0e0c145245166e0ac6b4bcbbc7f","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f4d145bb61331cf15b9a808c2d741622265b73","tid":399073,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fpostherpetic-neuralgia%2Fpages%2Fintroduction.aspx&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7416667f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/postherpetic-neuralgia/pages/introduction.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入面話年紀大先會咁<br />\n小弟27 歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMcp1403062%23t%3Darticle&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f493cf4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1403062#t=article</a><br />\nThere is currently no disease-modifying therapy for postherpetic neuralgia8; <span style=\"color: blue;\">thus, treatment is based on symptom control.</span> Because pain may persist for years or for life, medication is often required over prolonged periods. It is important to monitor the effect of interventions on pain intensity (with the methods described above) and to modify or discontinue treatments that do not result in appreciable pain relief or that have adverse effects in excess of the benefit.</blockquote><br />\n即係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGG<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7418a8