 />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb3ace5f17545b1377344c46a60a50122778412","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講睇西醫係睇唔好的 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 返大陸睇 用古方 個零兩個禮拜冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經停左西醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  宜家個個禮拜去針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b61ffd0ce60a257e825bb3e717ed8c0ceac9d00","tid":399073,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完你個名只可以講句抵死，有報應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果改名可以無事 即刻改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e203f57d027e5f852080bc88d826a8e79877f4","tid":399073,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"20生過 ，你依d 係因為過左黃金24定唔知72小時所以有後遺症神經痛，唔想番發建議早訓"},{"pid":"c0e11845792825f2db645ae13579fc60cc8e6bb8","tid":399073,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20生過 ，你依d 係因為過左黃金24定唔知72小時所以有後遺症神經痛，唔想番發建議早訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以好番，不過好似係慢慢散"},{"pid":"de0aac9d549cf043d2c4e22131df8aa8505c950b","tid":399073,"uid":967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"小學個陣生過係背脊 睇左好多次西醫都唔好<br />\n最後唔記得點解去左屋企樓下藥房 <br />\n咁岩佢又話佢有秘方<br />\n叫我老豆買支燒酒同硫黃粉比佢 <br />\n過一陣就整左一pat類似藥膏咁既野出黎<br />\n每日搽一次 一星期左右就好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b2f8d199b235ae242c789ec1d07c4de7f351e3","tid":399073,"uid":30663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"屋企兩個人都生過<br />\n瞬間返大陸搵個同鄉&quot;爆火&quot;<br />\n即時好左 真係秘技黎"},{"pid":"8b11c88f35b9a7240e2466dffecb1e88242121e9","tid":399073,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"我都生過，仲遲左去睇，生左好多，但唔痛，全部都係痕，好返就無事<br />\n<br />\n你係咪好遲好遲先睇？"},{"pid":"aec53b917d7df1c67b4ba5e26e86de59b505ab83","tid":399073,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學個陣生過係背脊 睇左好多次西醫都唔好<br />\n最後唔記得點解去左屋企樓下藥房 <br />\n咁岩佢又話佢有秘方<br />\n叫我老豆買支燒酒同硫黃粉比佢 <br />\n過一陣就整左一pat類似藥膏咁既野出黎<br />\n每日搽一次 一星期左右就好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學生水痘呀？<br />\n唔生水痘點會生蛇？"},{"pid":"e51fec834861e5b49f67b9178ba9f276801b3f09","tid":399073,"uid":46309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"食住止痛藥都一直痛?"}]}